p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-sub-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3330">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>gmp_sub()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$sub </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_sub</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"281474976710656"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"4294967296"</span><span style="color: #007700">); </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 2^48 - 2^32<br></span><span style="color: #007700">echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$sub</span><span style="color: #007700">) . </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">281470681743360</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div></div>
 * 
