 * <div id="function.gmp-mul" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">gmp_mul</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gmp_mul</span> — <span class="dc-title">Multiply numbers</span></p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mul-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gmp_mul</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num1</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num2</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Multiplies <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span> by <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span>   and returns the result.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mul-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       A number that will be multiplied by <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span>.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       A number that will be multiplied by <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span>.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mul-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mul-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3308">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>gmp_mul()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$mul </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_mul</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"12345678"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"2000"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$mul</span><span style="color: #007700">) . </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">24691356000</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div></div>
 * 
 * Multiply numbers
 * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/function.gmp-mul.php
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num1 <p>
 * A number that will be multiplied by <i>b</i>.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num2 <p>
 * A number that will be multiplied by <i>a</i>.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @return resource|GMP A GMP number resource.
 */
#[Pure]
function gmp_mul(GMP|string|int $num1, GMP|string|int $num2): GMP {}

/**
 * <div id="function.gmp-div-qr" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">gmp_div_qr</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gmp_div_qr</span> — <span class="dc-title">Divide numbers and get quotient and remainder</span></p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gmp-div-qr-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gmp_div_qr</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num1</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num2</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$rounding_mode</span><span class="initializer"> = <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/gmp.constants.php#constant.gmp-round-zero">GMP_ROUND_ZERO</a></span></strong></span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.array.php" class="type array" style="color:#EAB766">array</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   The function divides <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span> by <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-div-qr-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The number being divided.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The number that <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span> is being divided by.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">rounding_mode</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       See the <span class="function">{@link gmp_div_q()}</span> function for description       of the <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">rounding_mode</span> argument.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-div-qr-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns an <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.array.php" class="type array" style="color:#EAB766">array</a></span>, with the first   element being <span class="literal">[n/d]</span> (the integer result of the   division) and the second being <span class="literal">(n - [n/d] * d)</span>   (the remainder of the division).  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-div-qr-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3293">    <p><strong>示例 #1 Division of GMP numbers</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$a </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_init</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"0x41682179fbf5"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$res </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_div_qr</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$a</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"0xDEFE75"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">printf</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Result is: q - %s, r - %s"</span><span style="color: #007700">,<br>       </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$res</span><span style="color: #007700">[</span><span style="color: #9876AA">0</span><span style="color: #007700">]), </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$res</span><span style="color: #007700">[</span><span style="color: #9876AA">1</span><span style="color: #007700">]));<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.gmp-div-qr-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link gmp_div_q()} - Divide numbers</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link gmp_div_r()} - Remainder of the division of numbers</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
 * 
 * Divide numbers and get quotient and remainder
 * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/function.gmp-div-qr.php
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num1 <p>
 * The number being divided.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num2 <p>
 * The number that <i>n</i> is being divided by.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @param int $rounding_mode [optional] <p>
 * See the <b>gmp_div_q</b> function for description
