 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span>. The result is always non-negative, the   sign of <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span> is ignored.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mod-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num1</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num2</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The modulo that is being evaluated.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mod-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-mod-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3307">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>gmp_mod()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$mod </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_mod</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"8"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"3"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$mod</span><span style="color: #007700">) . </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">2</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div></div>
