 * <div id="function.gmp-powm" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">gmp_powm</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gmp_powm</span> — <span class="dc-title">Raise number into power with modulo</span></p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gmp-powm-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gmp_powm</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$exponent</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$modulus</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Calculate (<span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num</span> raised into power   <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">exponent</span>) modulo <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">modulus</span>. If   <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">exponent</span> is negative, result is undefined.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-powm-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The base number.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">exponent</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The positive power to raise the <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num</span>.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">modulus</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The modulo.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-powm-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   The new (raised) number, as a GMP number.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-powm-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3315">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>gmp_powm()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$pow1 </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_powm</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"2"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"31"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"2147483649"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_strval</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$pow1</span><span style="color: #007700">) . </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">2147483648</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div></div>
 * 
 * Raise number into power with modulo
 * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/function.gmp-powm.php
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num <p>
 * The base number.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @param resource|string|GMP $exponent <p>
 * The positive power to raise the <i>base</i>.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @param resource|string|GMP $modulus <p>
 * The modulo.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @return resource|GMP The new (raised) number, as a GMP number.
 */
#[Pure]
function gmp_powm(GMP|string|int $num, GMP|string|int $exponent, GMP|string|int $modulus): GMP {}

/**
 * <div id="function.gmp-perfect-square" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">gmp_perfect_square</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gmp_perfect_square</span> — <span class="dc-title">Perfect square check</span></p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gmp_perfect_square</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="type GMP" style="color:#EAB766">GMP</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$num</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.boolean.php" class="type bool" style="color:#EAB766">bool</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Check if a number is a perfect square.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The number being checked as a perfect square.      </p>      <p class="para"> <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.gmp.php" class="classname">GMP</a></span> 对象、<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 或 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>，可以按照跟在 <span class="function">{@link gmp_init()}</span> 中使用字符串并自动检测 base（即当 base 等于 0 时）相同的逻辑将其解释为数字。</p>      </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong> if <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">num</span> is a perfect square,   <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong> otherwise.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3312">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>gmp_perfect_square()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 3 * 3, perfect square<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"9"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// not a perfect square<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"7"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 1234567890 * 1234567890, perfect square<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">var_dump</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_perfect_square</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1524157875019052100"</span><span style="color: #007700">));<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">bool(true)<br>bool(false)<br>bool(true)</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.gmp-perfect-square-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link gmp_perfect_power()} - Perfect power check</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link gmp_sqrt()} - Calculate square root</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link gmp_sqrtrem()} - Square root with remainder</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
 * 
 * Perfect square check
 * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/function.gmp-perfect-square.php
 * @param resource|string|GMP $num <p>
 * The number being checked as a perfect square.
 * </p>
 * <p>It can be either a GMP number resource, or a
 * numeric string given that it is possible to convert the latter to a number.</p>
 * @return bool <b>TRUE</b> if <i>a</i> is a perfect square,
 * <b>FALSE</b> otherwise.
 */
