v class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$cmp1 </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_cmp</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1234"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1000"</span><span style="color: #007700">); </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// greater than<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$cmp2 </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_cmp</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1000"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1234"</span><span style="color: #007700">); </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// less than<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$cmp3 </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gmp_cmp</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1234"</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"1234"</span><span style="color: #007700">); </span><span style="color: #FF8000">// equal to<br><br></span><span style="color: #007700">echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$cmp1</span><span style="color: #DD0000"> </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$cmp2</span><span style="color: #DD0000"> </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$cmp3</span><span style="color: #DD0000">\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>   </div>   <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>   <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">1&nbsp;-1&nbsp;0</blockquote></